<li id="cite_note-85"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-85">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">See <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20090908173201/http://www.gg.ca/heraldry/pub-reg/project-pic.asp?lang=e&amp;ProjectID=582&amp;ProjectElementID=2051">St. Paul's Cathedral</a>.</span>
</li>
